#CHIP YM2608
#CLOCK 7987200

; YM2608 (OPNA) FM Channels Test — 6× FM channels
;
; The YM2608 has 6 FM channels (similar to YM2612 found in Mega Drive),
; plus 3 SSG channels and ADPCM-A/B for sample playback.
;
; Tests FM functionality:
; - All 6 channels with independent melodies
; - Polyphonic playback
; - Envelope control

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; FM Channels 1-3: Main melody
c4 . d4 . e4 .

r4

; FM Channels 4-6: Counter-melody (offset by octave)
c3 . d3 . e3 .

r4

; All 6 channels together
c4 & d4 & e4 & c3 & d3 & e3 .

r2

#END
